[It appears that more food handlers are being reported to be infected with HAV in Michigan as compared to California. It seems past the time when all food handlers in the USA should be required to have received the HAV vaccine. Healthcare workers are required to receive a variety of vaccines, in part to protect them but also, to minimize risks to the hospitalized population. - Mod.LL

